title: Revised scoping study for $205 million phosphate mine doubles expected mine life (Engineers Australia)
text: ( Source : Engineers Australia ) Potash West has started a Pre-Feasibility Study for the $205 million Dinner Hill phosphate mine in Western Australia , encouraged by the results of a revised scoping study which doubles the expected mine life
